description: Welcome to 607 E 2nd Street, a well-maintained single-family home offering two levels of finished living space above a two-car garage, plus an unfinished attic for future expansion. The first floor features a guest bedroom, a full bathroom, and a bright kitchen with beautiful countertops and a stylish backsplash. An open living and dining area leads to a private back deck, ideal for morning coffee or entertaining.The second floor includes two additional bedrooms, a well-appointed bathroom, and a convenient laundry closet, along with access to a second private deck. The top floor offers an unfinished attic providing excellent potential for future living space or additional storage. Located in the heart of South Boston, this home is close to beaches, parks, neighborhood restaurants, and shops, offering both convenience and a vibrant lifestyle.
